        or <a href="https://www.gamcare.org.uk" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">GamCare</a>.
      </p>
      <p class="rg disclose">
        Model predictions and "edges" are estimates and may be wrong. No affiliate or
        referral relationship with any sportsbook; odds are shown for comparison only.
        See <a href="/policy">policy &amp; disclosures</a>, the
        <a href="/methodology">methodology &amp; tamper-evident ledger</a>,
        or follow new edges via <a href="/feed.xml">RSS</a>.
      </p>
      <p class="foot-meta">
        <span>FIFA World Cup 2026 · USA · Canada · Mexico</span>
        <span class="dotsep" aria-hidden="true">/</span>
        <span>Personal betting-analysis dashboard</span>
        <span class="dotsep" aria-hidden="true">/</span>
        <span>© {year}</span>
      </p>
    </footer>
    <MobileNav />
  </body>
</html>
